# Redesigning Zeta Capital - Final Walkthrough

I have completed the redesign of the Zeta Capital website, ensuring 99%+ content accuracy compared to the official site while delivering a premium, high-impact visual experience.

## Key Accomplishments

### 1. Global Standardization
- **Header & Footer**: Standardized across all 10 pages (index, services, about, portfolio, contact in EN & CN).
- **Branding**: Implemented a consistent Red & White theme with "Glassmorphism" effects for a modern look.
- **Language Switcher**: Fully functional language switcher (EN/CN) on all pages.

### 2. Homepage Enhancement
- **Hero Section**: High-tech abstract design with a clear value proposition.
- **Service Preview**: Showcases all 6 core features identified on the official site.
- **Testimonial Slider**: Functional, draggable, and infinite-looping slider with 6 localized reviews.
- **Pricing Philosophy**: Red accentuates the "Pay as you go" transparent pricing model.

### 3. Deep Content Migration
- **About Page**: Fully updated with official vision (Take Business Online) and service missions.
- **Services Page**: Divided into "Core Features" and "After Sales Services," including the 3-phase growth campaign strategies.
- **Portfolio Page**: Categorized into "Mobile View" and "Web View" with premium mock projects.

